{"tid":420072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務院官網撤中華民國國旗  馬英九：政府應趕快交涉","createTime":"2017-10-01T05:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T05:51:18.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"99454993e85167f28e8043b07c17782b42aad44c","tid":420072,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"美國務院官網撤我國旗 馬英九：政府應趕快交涉<br />\n<br />\n2017/10/01 11:38&nbsp;1361<br />\n<br />\n國民黨第20屆中常委選舉今登場，共有49人角逐32席票選中常委。前總統馬英九上午到國民黨中央黨部投票，面對媒體詢問台美關係越來越差怎麼辦？馬英九表示，「再觀察看看，」至於近日美國國務院官網改版，但介紹台灣的頁面上，中華民國的國旗卻消失不見，面對媒體詢問，馬英九只簡短回說，「要趕快去交涉」，就快步離去。<br />\n<br />\n雙十節國慶即將到來，馬英九面對媒體詢問也表示，自己將會出席國慶典禮。<br />\n（余祥／台北報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171001/1214665/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171001%2F1214665%2F&d=124MPmTb5GpcFqLGG2F%2FZE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=31d4c634\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171001/1214665/</a>"},{"pid":"9f1593cc847f4f75f580490dd0dc50bc0cafdfa6","tid":420072,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"美國只係遵從&quot;一個中國政策&quot;"},{"pid":"67c4d890463d77c5c041b698817b00cb6a86a470","tid":420072,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"當年中國官員到台訪問<br />\n馬政府下令撤國旗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}